fields.body:
No server and no special skills required!

How? 

Nuntio CMS runs on [Google App Engine](http://code.google.com/intl/pl/appengine/) on Google infrastructure, and it's [free to start](http://code.google.com/intl/pl/appengine/docs/billing.html), even run for free if your site won't get much traffic! 

Nutio CMS is designed with simplicity in mind, this includes setup. There are only few simple steps to complete, to get your site up and running.
fields.author: test@example.com
